import { Row, Container, CounterValue, Content } from "./styles"
import ButtonCounter from "../../Components/ButtonCounter"

function Marmita() {
    


    return (<>

        <Container>
            <Content>

                <Row>
                        <ButtonCounter>T</ButtonCounter>
                        <CounterValue>1</CounterValue>
                        <ButtonCounter>P</ButtonCounter>

                </Row>

            </Content>
        </Container>
    
    
    </>)
}


export {Marmita}
